572
00:32:39,340 --> 00:32:40,100
Let's go, Jinglan.

573
00:32:41,540 --> 00:32:42,180
Your Highness.

574
00:32:53,980 --> 00:32:54,700
Take care.

575
00:33:15,660 --> 00:33:16,500
Are you done gawking?

576
00:33:18,780 --> 00:33:19,500
No.

577
00:33:25,580 --> 00:33:26,540
I just

578
00:33:27,060 --> 00:33:28,540
