579
00:33:28,780 --> 00:33:31,380
He's giving accommodations
to exam candidates in Huajing.

580
00:33:32,140 --> 00:33:33,300
Earlier on, I've heard

581
00:33:33,700 --> 00:33:35,580
that he's just taking in candidates,

582
00:33:35,940 --> 00:33:37,260
but also people
who're trying to file complaints.

583
00:33:38,340 --> 00:33:41,060
