of Su Rongqing's.

595
00:34:09,980 --> 00:34:11,620
I'll just have
to put up a few acts with him

596
00:34:11,620 --> 00:34:12,860
to earn Consort Rou's trust.

597
00:34:12,940 --> 00:34:14,460
