600
00:34:20,380 --> 00:34:21,140
Of course.

601
00:34:24,020 --> 00:34:24,980
Without Su Rongqing,

602
00:34:24,980 --> 00:34:26,420
Consort Rou is barely a threat.

603
00:34:26,700 --> 00:34:28,060
If Prince Su and she are gone,

604
00:34:28,060 --> 00:34:29,380
Su Rongqing will never

605
00:34:29,380 --> 00:34:30,540
defeat His Highness on his own

606
