623
00:36:21,140 --> 00:36:22,580
You may rise, Mr. Cui.

624
00:36:22,860 --> 00:36:23,580
Thank you, Your Highness.

625
00:36:24,860 --> 00:36:26,060
I heard

626
00:36:26,060 --> 00:36:28,340
