628
00:36:33,260 --> 00:36:33,860
Yes.

629
00:36:35,850 --> 00:36:39,530
So, why are you here, Mr. Cui?

630
00:36:42,540 --> 00:36:45,540
His Highness offered me
a fifth-ranked position.

631
00:36:46,260 --> 00:36:48,500
But your messenger told me

632
00:36:48,700 --> 00:36:51,220
that Prince Su would double the offer.

633
00:36:51,940 --> 00:36:54,380
Therefore, I'm here.

634
00:36:55,860 --> 00:36:57,940
