640
00:37:11,460 --> 00:37:12,740
Since you're so candid, Your Highness,

641
00:37:12,940 --> 00:37:15,060
I shall be frank.

642
00:37:16,580 --> 00:37:17,620
Your Highness,

643
00:37:18,060 --> 00:37:20,980
would you like
to have the Inspectorate Office?

644
00:37:28,020 --> 00:37:30,420
I know very well that you have

645
00:37:30,620 --> 00:37:32,260
many advisors by your side.

646
00:37:32,900 --> 00:37:35,660
As such, I do not come empty-handed.

647
00:37:36,060 --> 00:37:37,100
Complaining about the Crown Prince

648
00:37:37,580 --> 00:37:39,140
is just the stepping stone.

649
00:37:39,700 --> 00:37:41,060
The Inspectorate Office

650
00:37:41,500 --> 00:37:44,180
will be my real gift, Your Highness.

651
00:37:45,700 --> 00:37:47,340
Would you like

652
00:37:48,980 --> 00:37:51,460
to receive this gift, Your Highness?

653
00:37:56,660 --> 00:37:57,500
I found out

654
00:37:57,820 --> 00:37:59,620
that since early this year,

655
00:37:59,620 --> 00:38:01,140
Su Rongqing has been taking care

656
00:38:01,220 --> 00:38:03,260
of scholars who came
to Huajing to attend the examination.

657
00:38:03,860 --> 00:38:06,260
Ordinary candidates will stay
at the yard you've seen.

658
00:38:06,580 --> 00:38:07,940
Those who wish to remedy injustices

659
00:38:08,100 --> 00:38:10,060
