660
00:38:13,540 --> 00:38:14,740
Why is he...

661
00:38:16,460 --> 00:38:17,260
doing this?

662
00:38:18,260 --> 00:38:19,060
I don't know yet.

663
00:38:20,220 --> 00:38:21,660
Interestingly,

664
00:38:22,900 --> 00:38:25,340
Mr. Pei's men are among them.

665
00:38:37,220 --> 00:38:38,340
Tell Cui Yulang

666
00:38:38,940 --> 00:38:39,620
to speed up

667
00:38:39,900 --> 00:38:42,540
the plan with Consort Rou.

668
00:38:43,060 --> 00:38:43,660
Yes, Your Highness.

669
00:38:50,020 --> 00:38:50,820
Your Highness.

670
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:54,460
A scholar came to the office

671
00:38:54,540 --> 00:38:56,740
