his examination candidature.

672
00:38:56,980 --> 00:38:58,020
I brought him here.

673
00:39:02,380 --> 00:39:04,260
Greetings, Your Highness.

674
00:39:04,900 --> 00:39:06,060
Are you Chen Houzhao?

675
00:39:06,540 --> 00:39:07,540
Yes.

676
00:39:08,340 --> 00:39:09,540
Do you have the written complaint?

677
00:39:10,060 --> 00:39:11,140
I have written it.

678
00:39:18,540 --> 00:39:21,060
I did go to the Su Family,

679
00:39:21,220 --> 00:39:22,980
but when I was there,

680
00:39:24,060 --> 00:39:24,980
they tried

681
00:39:26,860 --> 00:39:28,020
to buy me off.

682
00:39:28,700 --> 00:39:29,820
What

683
00:39:30,540 --> 00:39:32,020
did they do?

684
00:39:32,700 --> 00:39:35,220
They tried to silence me.

685
00:39:35,900 --> 00:39:37,340
Why did you come to me, then?

686
00:39:38,060 --> 00:39:39,180
A friend of mine

687
00:39:39,540 --> 00:39:41,420
told me that you could be trusted.

688
00:39:42,460 --> 00:39:43,620
You are willing to trust me?

689
00:39:45,060 --> 00:39:46,060
Yes, I am.

690
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:50,140
Su Rongqing
has taken in aggrieved individuals

691
00:39:50,660 --> 00:39:52,020
but has forbidden them
from filing complaints.

692
00:39:52,980 --> 00:39:54,460
What is he trying to do?

693
00:40:04,020 --> 00:40:06,220
Take the money and leave Huajing.

694
00:40:06,940 --> 00:40:08,140
By Huajing Moat,

695
00:40:08,140 --> 00:40:09,980
there is an old man called San.

696
00:40:10,820 --> 00:40:13,060
Board his boat and leave.

697
00:40:13,540 --> 00:40:15,700
The boat will sink
when approaching Zhang County.

698
00:40:15,820 --> 00:40:17,380
You will swim to the shore with San.

699
00:40:17,460 --> 00:40:18,660
Someone will take you to safety.

700
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:21,540
Lay low for a while

701
00:40:22,500 --> 00:40:23,620
and wait for my order.

702
00:40:25,540 --> 00:40:26,540
Yes, Your Highness.

703
00:40:26,700 --> 00:40:27,940
Thank you.

704
00:40:35,020 --> 00:40:38,220
Your Highness,
what are you trying to do?

705
00:40:38,340 --> 00:40:40,060
You will serve someone else soon.

706
00:40:40,700 --> 00:40:41,980
Get ready.

707
00:40:42,020 --> 00:40:45,060
You're giving up on the office for now?

708
00:40:48,650 --> 00:40:50,950
[Mingyue Palace]

709
00:40:55,660 --> 00:40:57,540
Your Highness, Prince Su,

710
00:40:57,820 --> 00:41:00,060
please seek justice for me.

711
00:41:01,540 --> 00:41:03,060
What is the problem?

712
00:41:03,260 --> 00:41:04,140
Tell us.

713
00:41:06,340 --> 00:41:09,380
Your Highness, I have a friend
from my hometown

714
00:41:09,940 --> 00:41:10,900
called Chen Houzhao.

715
00:41:11,540 --> 00:41:12,860
A local squire took

716
00:41:12,940 --> 00:41:15,540
his candidature
for the spring examination,

717
00:41:16,180 --> 00:41:17,660
so he came to me in Huajing
to seek help.

718
00:41:18,580 --> 00:41:19,860
I redirected him

719
00:41:19,860 --> 00:41:21,980
to Princess Pingyue.

720
00:41:22,940 --> 00:41:24,260
Just as I expected,

721
00:41:24,500 --> 00:41:26,980
after Her Highness received
the written complaint,

722
00:41:27,540 --> 00:41:29,060
she sent him out of Huajing.

723
00:41:29,940 --> 00:41:30,940
And now,

724
00:41:31,340 --> 00:41:34,580
I can't even locate the boat
they used to send him out.

725
00:41:36,060 --> 00:41:38,420
Is this true?

726
00:41:41,100 --> 00:41:42,140
Chen Houzhao

727
00:41:42,420 --> 00:41:44,060
left this written complaint to me.

728
00:41:48,260 --> 00:41:49,340
Please take a look.

729
00:41:54,460 --> 00:41:55,500
I believe

730
00:41:55,980 --> 00:41:58,540
you can summon Princess Pingyue

731
00:41:58,660 --> 00:42:00,940
here tomorrow

732
00:42:01,340 --> 00:42:02,940
and show her the written complaint.

733
00:42:03,060 --> 00:42:03,860
After that,

734
00:42:04,260 --> 00:42:06,660
we can expose this in court.

735
00:42:11,580 --> 00:42:12,660
Your Highness,

736
00:42:13,340 --> 00:42:16,500
do you know why Princess Pingyue
wanted to kill Chen Houzhao?

737
00:42:19,940 --> 00:42:20,940
Pray tell.

738
00:42:21,660 --> 00:42:22,620
Stand up and speak.

739
00:42:24,180 --> 00:42:25,060
Thank you, Your Highness.

740
00:42:25,620 --> 00:42:29,260
Pei, brew some tea for Mr. Cui.

741
00:42:29,460 --> 00:42:30,340
Yes, Your Highness.

742
00:42:35,540 --> 00:42:36,220
Your Highness,

743
00:42:36,700 --> 00:42:40,500
Princess Pingyue
is the Crown Prince's sister, after all.

744
00:42:40,820 --> 00:42:42,580
While they are against
the noble families on the surface,

745
00:42:43,060 --> 00:42:44,380
they are one of them.

746
00:42:45,050 --> 00:42:45,810
Thus,

747
00:42:46,020 --> 00:42:47,740
she could investigate
the Qin Family's case

748
00:42:47,980 --> 00:42:49,260
and the military provisions
and funds case,

749
00:42:49,620 --> 00:42:51,380
but she cannot harm the foundation
of the noble families.

750
00:42:51,700 --> 00:42:53,180
His Majesty implemented

751
00:42:53,660 --> 00:42:56,660
the imperial examination
to balance noble families.

752
00:42:57,900 --> 00:43:00,700
There are so many people involved
in this case

753
00:43:01,340 --> 00:43:04,180
and she is in a precarious position.

754
00:43:04,700 --> 00:43:05,980
Therefore, she will not take the case.

755
00:43:07,060 --> 00:43:08,460
Not only will she reject it,

756
00:43:08,700 --> 00:43:10,020
but she also has to protect the position
of noble families.

757
00:43:10,660 --> 00:43:13,540
If those noble families fall,
so will the Crown Prince.

758
00:43:14,420 --> 00:43:17,540
Thus, she must kill Chen Houzhao.

759
00:43:19,540 --> 00:43:21,700
You already knew
that she'd kill Chen Houzhao

760
00:43:21,860 --> 00:43:23,540
before you sent him to her?

761
00:43:25,620 --> 00:43:27,540
I said I'd give you and Prince Su

762
00:43:27,820 --> 00:43:29,580
the Inspectorate Office.

763
00:43:30,180 --> 00:43:31,220
Did you think

764
00:43:31,740 --> 00:43:33,220
I was joking?

765
00:43:34,620 --> 00:43:36,380
We lured her into killing Chen Houzhao.

766
00:43:36,540 --> 00:43:37,940
With that, we got something on her.

767
00:43:38,460 --> 00:43:39,100
Then,

768
00:43:39,500 --> 00:43:41,380
we can force her to take
the wronged candidate case.

769
00:43:42,260 --> 00:43:44,020
She doesn't want to handle the case.

770
00:43:44,700 --> 00:43:46,260
Besides, we got something on her.

771
00:43:47,180 --> 00:43:48,620
Leaving the Inspectorate Office

772
00:43:48,820 --> 00:43:50,580
is her best option.

773
00:43:51,220 --> 00:43:52,060
Once she's gone,

774
00:43:52,380 --> 00:43:54,100
someone has to run the office.

775
00:43:54,740 --> 00:43:56,460
Whoever is willing
to investigate this case

776
00:43:57,060 --> 00:44:00,620
is the new leader
of the Inspectorate Office.

777
00:44:04,180 --> 00:44:05,020
Your Highness,

778
00:44:05,540 --> 00:44:08,820
His Majesty appreciates your background
as a commoner.

779
00:44:09,260 --> 00:44:11,260
