782
00:44:18,580 --> 00:44:21,580
Princess Pingyue was investigating
the noble families.

783
00:44:21,900 --> 00:44:23,140
Thus, she was allowed
to establish the Inspectorate Office.

784
00:44:23,740 --> 00:44:26,660
If you want to earn His Majesty's favor,

785
00:44:27,460 --> 00:44:31,540
